Australian Immunisation Register Vaccine

https://healthterminologies.gov.au/fhir/ValueSet/australian-immunisation-register-vaccine-1

The Australian Immunisation Register Vaccine value set includes values that may be used to represent a vaccine product according to the Australian Immunisation Register vaccine code formats.
